I"¬<h2 id="efficiency">Efficiency</h2>
<p>Option 1:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>if (output === 'file') {
    file.write (...)
} else if (output === 'console') {
    console.log (...)
}
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Option 2:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>fd.write (...)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Option 2 will be more efficient than option 1, regardless of whether you implement the code in a language like <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Rust</code> or <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">C++</code></p>

